text: Pracht is surname of: * Charles Frederick Pracht (1880 – 1950), a Republican member of the U.S. House of Representatives * Eva "Evi" Maria Pracht (born 1937, Würzburg), a German-Canadian horse rider * Karl Brandler-Pracht, astrologer * Karl Robert Pracht (1878, Mulhouse - 1961, Karlsruhe), a German composer and music educator == See also == * Pracht, a municipality in the district of Altenkirchen, Rhineland-Palatinate, western Germany Category:German-language surnames
